episodes.title: Actor Andrew Keegan Responds to CULT LEADER Claims | E! News
episodes.description:
The 10 Things I Hate About You actor visits the Pod Meets World podcast and addresses allegations he ran a cult a few years back! Andrew Keegan says he was putting down "tens of thousands of dollars" at one point to get the Venice, Calif. spiritual group up and running.

Full Story: https://www.eonline.com/news/1395054/10-things-i-hate-about-you-actor-andrew-keegan-responds-to-claims-he-ran-a-cult?source=youtube&medium=enews
